Series II. Unprocessed digital media formats

This series includes digital media formats in the collection from which files have not yet been processed due to the lack of necessary hardware. These include 5.25 inch floppy disks, Digital Audio Tape (DAT), and Mini DV. The container list identifies the content as identified on the media labels.
